    <p class="text-gray-300">and using that  <span class="math">\\rho_0^2 +\\rho_0\\cdot \\delta &#x27; - \\delta&#x27;^2 -\\rho_0 + \\delta &#x27; = 0</span>  , we obtain that the latter term equals</p>

