    <h2 id="sec-28" class="text-2xl font-bold">6.1 Brakedown's 128 bit large field</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-300">As a first example, we compare the results of our formulas with the example parameters from  <span class="math">\\mathrm{[GLS^{+}21]}</span> . We approximate the relative overall cost, in field operations per domain size  <span class="math">n</span> , by the formula</p>

