    <p class="text-gray-300">However, even though choosing a tangent bound for matrix  <span class="math">A</span>  does not have much impact it still can yield a slight improvement. For the first two configurations in Table 1 we are able to take different scaling factors  <span class="math">\\alpha</span> , and obtain reduced  <span class="math">c_{n}</span>  as well  <span class="math">d_{n}</span> :</p>

